28dc57b2-cb28-4c37-8d61-dd5af131184e	\N	en	Helsinki: "Beitii Falastiin - My home Palestine" Panel Discussion	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.17339	2026-01-05 11:55:51.17339	helsinki-beitii-falastiin-my-home-palestine-panel-discussion	published	As part of the Ruskeat tytöt, Kodin kaikuja exhibition in Stoa, Helsinki\n\n12th of December at 6-7:30 PM\n\n"Beitii Falastiin - My home Palestine" Panel Discussion\n\nThis panel explores what Palestine means to those who call it home. Panelists include journalist Randa Aldawoudi, activist Yehia Al-Sayed, multi- instrumentalist Tareq Abboushi, and Finnish- Palestinian activist Lina Jarallah. Facilitated by Shareef Askar, the evening includes a musical performance by Tareq Abboushi.\n\nThe event is free of charge.	\N	havu.laasko	havu.laasko	2024-12-11 02:00:00	\N	\N	2024-12-11 02:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/1-5.jpeg	\N	[]	[]	[]
