ba7d7cce-c395-4e78-bad0-951fe00a750e	\N	en	Helsinki: Vappu march	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.201014	2026-01-05 11:55:51.201014	helsinki-vappu-march	published	This year too, we are forming a Palestine block in the Helsinki Workers' May Day march! Welcome to join us in defending everyone's human rights as a united strong front.\n\nThe march will gather on May 1, at Hakaniemi Market Square at 11 am and will head towards Kansalaistori at 11:15 am. Program at Kansalaistori will end at 2:30 pm. Come early, because there will be a lot of people there. You can find us under the Palestinian flags, of course! 🇵🇸🇵🇸🇵🇸\n\nIt is an important moment to remind decision-makers about fair municipal and government policies, taking human rights into account in Finnish defense procurement, and the realization of Palestinian rights!\n\nThe event is organized in cooperation with the SAK's local organization in the Helsinki Metropolitan Area, the Helsinki Social Democrats and the Helsinki Left.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-04-28 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-04-28 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Copy-of-Copy-of-Tampere-Ig-posts.zip-15.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
c186f789-3c78-4ed4-8688-5c4690daad80	4c9010f0-61e9-4e10-bb83-7f0548f0c429	en	Helsinki: Café Palestine	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.201442	2026-01-05 11:55:51.201442	helsinki-cafe-palestine-4	published	Welcome to Café Palestine on Sunday, May 4 at 5-8 pm at Oranssi (Kaasutehtaankatu 1, Suvilahti).\n\nCafé Palestine is organized in collaboration between Sumud Helsinki and Palcif (Finnish Palestinian community). This time we'll have an introduction from Palcif and hear stories from it's experienced members. How was it to be a Palestinian in Finland in the 90's and what was activism like back then? We will also have some Palestinian activities like tatreez, Henna, palestinian traditional songs and DABKEH.\n\nCoffee, tea and Palestinian snacks will be offered.\n\nBefore the café (4-5 pm) we will have an info session for newcomers. Do you want to join a working group in Sumud Helsinki chapter? Come hear more in detail what each group does!\n\nAccessibility info:\n\nOranssi's entrance, event space and toilets are at street level and are accessible with support devices of all sizes. However, some higher doorway thresholds and sloping ramps may be difficult for people using manual wheelchairs. The toilets are gender-neutral.\n\nأهلاً بكم في مقهى فلسطين يوم الأحد 4.5.2025 من الساعة 17:00 إلى 20:00\n\nتنظيم مقهى فلسطين بالتعاون بين جمعية صمود هلسنكي والجالية الفلسطينية الفنلندية ( PALCIF ). هذه المرة، سنتعرف على الجالية الفلسطينية في فنلندة (PALCIF) ونستمع إلى قصص من أعضائها ذوي الخبرة. كيف كانت الحياة الفلسطينية في فنلندا في التسعينيات، وكيف كان النشاط السياسي آنذاك؟\n\nيتخلل الفعالية بعض الأنشطة الفلسطينية كالتطريز والحِنّة وبعض الاغاني التراثية الفلسطينية بالإضافة إلى الدبكة الفلسطينية\n\nسيتم تقديم القهوة والشاي الفلسطيني بالإضافة إلى سناك فلسطيني خفيف\n\nقبل المقهى (من الساعة ١٦-١٧) سيكون هناك جلسة تعريفية للقادمين الجدد. هل ترغبون بالانضمام إلى مجموعة عمل في فرع جمعية صمود هلسنكي؟\n\nتعالوا واستمعوا إلى المزيد من التفاصيل حول أنشطة كل مجموعة\n\nمعلومات  الوصول \n\nمدخل أورانسي في قاعة الفعاليات\n\nدورات المياه كلها على مستوى الشارع وهي مهيأة للوصول إليها باستخدام أدوات الدعم من جميع الأحجام\n\nومع ذلك، قد تكون بعض العتبات المرتفعة عند المداخل والمنحدرات المائلة صعبة للأشخاص الذين يستخدمون الكراسي المتحركة اليدوية\n\n دورات المياه محايدة من حيث النوع الاجتماعي	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-04-28 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-04-28 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/cafe-palestine.jpg	\N	[]	[]	[]
ceb2798f-e394-4afb-a83d-8e35b97345a1	\N	en	Kouvola: Local chapter's meeting	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.202095	2026-01-05 11:55:51.202095	kouvola-local-chapters-meeting	published	Sumud's local chapter in Kouvola will organise a meeting on Tuesday, May 6, at 5-6:30 pm at Monikulttuurikeskus Saaga. The meeting will focus on catching up and planning activities for the rest of the year. For more information, send an email to sumudkouvola(at)proton.me. Welcome!	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-04-28 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-04-28 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Screenshot-2025-04-28-at-14-41-14-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
8c8f6731-3def-4006-b85d-c41dccf62438	\N	en	Kuopio: Vappu march	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.202488	2026-01-05 11:55:51.202488	kuopio-vappu-march	published	Join us at the open free Palestine block in May Day march in Kuopio! The march will start at 12 at Kuopio Market Square, on the side of Puijonkatu.\n\nTake a stand, raise our voices and defend our and others rights. This May Day, let's remind decision-makers that there are many of us, and that we do care what kind of Kuopio, Finland and world we live in. There is always hope, and that hope begins with us!\n\nIf you have not yet marched for Palestine, this is a good opportunity to come, take a stance for human rights, and learn about the Palestine movement.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-04-28 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-04-28 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Screenshot-2025-04-28-at-15-12-40-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
