0f234307-d987-48fc-ac4b-9afc2f49487c	78c906f7-8bd5-4464-a909-636ed888e242	en	Tampere: Bake Sale	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.228105	2026-01-05 11:55:51.228105	tampere-bake-sale-2	published	Tampere with Palestine organises a bake sale on Saturday, August 16, at 2-5 pm at Laukontori in Tampere .\n\nSweet and savoury snacks will be served. Delicious falafels will also make a return! Falafels are sold in bags (no heating available on site). Crafts4Gaza support products for sale, too.\n\nProceeds will be sent to Gaza and Sudan.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-08-13 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-08-13 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2025-08-13-at-11-32-19-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
ef852ecc-4cf7-47cb-8769-436d873da666	b43492d7-ea65-4f34-ab97-021284055cd8	en	Helsinki: Festival of Resistance(s)	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.212136	2026-01-05 11:55:51.212136	helsinki-festival-of-resistances	published	The Festival of Resistance(s) on Tuesday, May 27, from 11 a.m. onwards at the Kansalaistori Square in Helsinki.\n\nThe Festival of Resistance(s) is a free and open, one-day event that acts as a platform for joining the voices of artists and various Non-Governmental Organizations in a call for a socially sustainable future and discussion on how the themes of (de)colonialism and human rights connect with justice and peace.\n\nCentered around the theme of resistance to occupation, the festival aims to raise awareness of occupied territories, minds, and bodies around the world that are denied their right to self-determination - an integral element of basic human rights (UN).	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-05-22 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-05-22 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Screenshot-2025-05-22-at-09-49-07-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
