ebc13e88-6f62-4c9d-8ca4-7daeb430fcfe	\N	en	Tampere: Market of Possibilities	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.212915	2026-01-05 11:55:51.212915	tampere-market-of-possibilities	published	Do you want more information about Sumud operations? Would you like to get to know the vast network of communities and organizations?\n\nSumud Tampere is participating in the Market of possibilities and social forum. You can expect our merch table, communications between organizations as well as Palestine and peace themed conversations.\n\nThe event is held on 29.5.2025 at 11-16 in Työväenmuseo Werstas (Väinö Linnan aukio 8).\n\nThe events gather local organizations, communities and networks that aim to develop global equality, people’s wellness as well as the realization of human rights and human value.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-05-26 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-05-26 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Screenshot-2025-05-26-at-10-54-09-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
