69f94a7e-4e84-4037-894b-f07495bd0dd3	\N	en	Helsinki: Pots and Pans –  March Against the Genocide	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.224543	2026-01-05 11:55:51.224543	helsinki-pots-and-pans-march-against-the-genocide	published	Palestinian Community in Finland and Finnish-Arab Friendship Society will organise a Pots and Pans march against the genocide on Saturday, July 12, at 3 pm at the Railway Station Square in Helsinki.\n\nGaza is starving – Save Gaza's children!\n\nJoin us in demanding justice and showing solidarity for the suffering children of Gaza. We can not be silent while Palestinians are being starved! Bring a little pot, pan, spoon or some other cutlery with you.\n\nThe march will move to the Helsinki Market Square where we will hear a speech about the situation in Gaza and about the urgent actions required to stop the genocide.\n\nSumud is a supporter of the demonstration.\n\nThe police is present to secure safety.\n\nRacist, sexist and other discriminatory symbols and slogans are prohibited.\n\nThere will be de-escalators at the demonstration who you can turn to if you feel unsafe or something worries you.\n\nThere will also be chanters whose chants you can join but you can also take part in the demonstration silently if that feels more natural. All ways of being present are valuable.\n\nBring signs, friends and a voice for justice with you!	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-07-08 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-07-08 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/WhatsApp-Image-2025-07-04-at-20.30.19.jpeg	\N	[]	[]	[]
