76994fc9-7bbe-476d-932c-4298522870f8	022c3954-57fb-4848-b783-d8e8ee608853	en	Helsinki: Human Chain Against the Genocide	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.229237	2026-01-05 11:55:51.229237	helsinki-ihmisketju-kansanmurhaa-vastaan-2	published	Finnish-Arab Friendship Society and Palestinian Community in Finland will organise a human chain against the genocide on Saturday, August 23 at 3 pm at Aleksanterinkatu, Helsinki.\n\nJoin us to form the POTS & PANS human chain against Palestinian genocide and starvation.\n\nLet us show together that we do not accept violence, occupation, ethnic cleansing, starvation or apartheid!\n\nThe police will be present to monitor security. Racist, sexist or otherwise discriminatory symbols and slogans are not allowed.\n\nThere are de-escalators at the event who you can turn to if you feel unsafe or if you have any concerns.\n\nWe also have chanters who you can join in with the slogans - but you can also protest quietly if you feel more comfortable. Every way of being present is valuable.\n\nBring a pot, a pan, a spoon, a plate, signs, friends and a voice for justice!	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-08-19 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-08-19 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2025-08-19-at-15-34-51-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
