31e65a38-deae-417f-8868-fb3042e0a1b2	\N	en	The Encampments – Screening &amp; discussion with Omar Barghouti	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.230226	2026-01-05 11:55:51.230226	the-encampments-screening-discussion-with-omar-barghouti	published	BDS Finland and Cinema Orion invite you to the Finnish premiere of the documentary The Encampments.\n\nThrough exclusive footage and intimate interviews, THE ENCAMPMENTS provides an unprecedented look at one of the most significant student movements in modern history. The film captures the passion, resilience, and challenges faced by students who risked everything to demand justice.\n\nThe screening will be followed by a panel discussion centered around young people’s activism, academic and cultural boycott, and university encampments in Finland. The panel includes a very special participation from Omar Barghouti, Co-Founder of the Palestinian-led BDS movement, as well as Students for Palestine activist Vilja Hermansson and Researchers Antti Tarvainen and Nitin Sawhney.\n\nThe ticket sales money will be donated to Sumud the Finnish-Palestine network and allocated\nfor campaigning and raising awareness about BDS.\n\nYou can choose the ticket type from following options: 9,50€ / 12€ /20€.\n\nBuy tickets: https://cinemaorion.fi/elokuvat/the-encampments/	\N	havu.laasko	havu.laasko	2025-08-20 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-08-20 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/3.jpeg	\N	[]	[]	[]
