d9dc7877-6808-4c67-b85e-9c6370c8cae5	f84ab274-1d7c-4f8a-b4b1-b2b42412277a	en	Tampere: Discussion	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.231392	2026-01-05 11:55:51.231392	tampere-keskustelutilaisuus	published	Aseistakieltäytyjäliitto, Pirkanmaan Rauhanpuolustajat and Sadankomitea will organise a Rauhanklubi event on Monday, August 25 at 5:30-7:30 pm at Arttelin Ekokolo (Mustalahdenkatu 22, Tampere) .\n\nIn January 2024, the International Criminal Court (ICJ) obliged all countries to "use all possible measures" to prevent Israel from committing genocide.\nWhat concrete steps has Finland taken to restrain Israel since it launched its campaign of destruction in autumn 2023?\n\nSigned a major missile deal with Israel in December 2023\n\nSuspended funding for UNRWA, the only effective aid agency in Gaza, over unfounded suspicions\n\nSending a high-level representative of the Defence Forces to Israel in September 2024 to promote military relations between the two countries and to visit operational areas\n\nWhy does Finland ignore international law and allow genocide? The moderator of the discussion will be civil society activist Erkki Tuomioja.\n\nWe follow the safer space guidelines, and coffee and snacks are available. Free admission.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-08-22 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-08-22 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Rauhanklubi-tampere.jpg	\N	[]	[]	[]
