ee9ed165-bf64-44e4-ab97-0a6f1e68324b	24713132-350a-45e4-999b-fec30a47fa74	en	Helsinki: Festival of Palestinian Culture	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.232566	2026-01-05 11:55:51.232566	helsinki-palestiinalaisen-kulttuurin-festivaali	published	Festival of Palestinian Culture on August 29-30 at the Caisa Cultural Centre (Kaikukatu 4B, Helsinki).\n\nFriday, August 29 at 17.30\nCaisa auditorium, Kaikukatu 4 B, Helsinki\nTickets 7€\n\nAs part of the two-day Festival of Palestinian Culture, Caisa will screen the powerful documentary Slingshot Hip Hop - the story of young artists in Gaza, the West Bank and the 1948 occupied Palestinian territory.\nAfter the screening, we will delve into the themes in a panel with hip hop artist Tariq Abu Nahel and other guests.\n\nCome and experience how music breaks down barriers and brings people together!\n\nSaturday, August 30\nCaisa, Kaikukatu 4 B, Helsinki\nThe event is free of charge, concert at 20:00 (15 € / 7 €)\n\nThe Festival of Palestinian Culture fills Caisa with flavours, art and a sense of community. The day will include workshops, literature, poetry, fashion, dance and a concert by Meera & Band in the evening.\n\nDuring the day:\nTatreez workshop (Palestinian embroidery)\nPalestinian food\nLiving library - hear Palestinian stories\nSpoken word poetry\nDabke dance\nMeera & Band concert in the evening\n\nThe exact schedule and programme at Caisa's website.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-08-23 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-08-23 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2025-08-23-at-20-41-28-1-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
4bba51c4-ec1f-4f26-b4d1-cf666544bba2	40c4f07a-82f1-4aa4-9f06-80994ae92eae	en	Turku Pride	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.232951	2026-01-05 11:55:51.232951	turku-pride	published	Turku with Palestine marches in Turku Pride Saturday 30 August as part of a radical bloc. The block will meet at the Old Market Square at 11 am and the procession will leave at 12 noon.\n\nIs the Pride movement suffering from a lack of rebellion? Do you want to demand total liberation for all, instead of hand-warming assimilation and acceptance? Turku with Palestine, queer anarchists and other comrades marched as a block at Turku Pride.\n\nOur requirements are:\n\nWe call for a re-politicisation of the Pride movement. Our existence is political and the demand for liberation we put forward is radical: we don't have to blend into the mainstream or settle for "being tolerated." We do not demand acceptance for the few, but total liberation for all.\n\nWe demand principled anti-Zionism from all queer and LGBTQ+ organisations. This demand is non-negotiable. We oppose all attempts to pinkwash imperialist oppression and know that the only way forward is a free Palestine, from the river to the sea.\n\nIn today's Finland, trans health care is decided by anti-gender "experts." We recognise the unacceptability of the situation, and reaffirm our absolute commitment to the struggle for transgender people's right to self-determination. Our demand is: Gatekeepers down! Trans liberation now!	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-08-26 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-08-26 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Screenshot-2025-08-26-at-10-04-20-1-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
