21457c7b-1906-4d5d-957d-2def503a3fa7	\N	en	Kuopio: Movie Screening	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.243461	2026-01-05 11:55:51.243461	kuopio-movie-screening	published	Kuopio for Palestine, Watan friendship association and Crafts4Gaza will screen the movie Slingshot Hip Hop on Thursday, September 11, at 20.30 at Kulttuurikonepaja, Kuopio.\n\nThe event is part of ANTI Festival’s project A Piece of Space: 106 hours assembly.\n\nA Piece of Space is an expanded assembly that transforms the Culture Workshop Konepaja into a temporary collective home: a public space that becomes a bedroom, a living room, a meeting point, a space where to cohabit and share responsibilities.\n\nMore info at antifestival.com\n\nThe Culture Workshop Kuopio is an apartheid free zone.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-09-10 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-09-10 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2025-09-10-at-16-38-34-1-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
