5b2a25dd-77cf-487a-a1da-03c777685e0f	\N	en	Helsinki: Discussion on Zionism, Imperialism and Resistance	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.244231	2026-01-05 11:55:51.244231	helsinki-discussion-on-zionism-imperialism-and-resistance	published	Discussion "Never Ending Wars - Resistance at Intersections of Orientalism, Imperialism, and Zionism" hosted by BDS Finland, No War on Iran and Nahlieli on Saturday, September 20, at 4-6 pm at Trans Library (Korppaanmäentie 21, Helsinki).\n\nPlease join us for a fruitful discussion in intersection of our struggles from Iran to Palestine, from Afghanistan to Kurdistan, here and everywhere. Why wars never end? What is the role of imperialism in creating this situation? What can we do about it? What can be called resistance? please bring your own questions and opinions to share with us.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-09-10 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-09-10 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2025-09-10-at-17-05-22-1-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
