bb926486-5149-4747-ac65-a9a4c8504290	\N	en	Turku: Run with Palestine Run Club	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.24845	2026-01-05 11:55:51.24845	turku-run-with-palestine-run-club	published	The Run with Palestine Turku run club runs in Turku every other Saturday at 2 pm, from Tuomiokirkontori to Turun linna and back! First run on 27.9.\n\nA run club to draw attention to the genocide, to show our solidarity and find community in others. A run club that offers space to release and process your emotions through movement!\n\nBiweekly on Saturday afternoons at 14:00, a 7,5 km route, starting and ending at Tuomiokirkontori, the route follows the river to the castle and back! Everyone is welcome to join at their own pace, for the whole route or a part of it!\n\nBring your sneakers, flags and signs! Wear your kuffiyeh or the colors of Palestine.\n\nThere’s no registration, just show up! Join, share, bring friends, spread the message.\n\nMore info will be posted on Instagram @runwithpalestineturku.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-09-19 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-09-19 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Screenshot-2025-09-19-at-10-42-11-Instagram.png	\N	[]	[]	[]
c20fb070-44c3-4fcb-b06b-5c1ed405acd9	161326a7-a9d2-4ecc-8566-bf37b8bfdc8b	en	Helsinki: Demonstration	\N	\N	2026-01-05 11:55:51.248883	2026-01-05 11:55:51.248883	helsinki-mielenosoitus-7	published	Global movement to Gaza Finland, Palcif and Nahlieli will organise a demonstration on Friday, September 26, at 3-4 pm at the Parliament House. The demonstration is supported by Sumud Helsinki, Finnish-Arab Friendship Society, Äitikapina, Crafts4Gaza ja Health for Palestine Finland.\n\nFINAL WAKE-UP CALL TO THE FINNISH GOVERNMENT\n\nBring your alarm clock: Your voice, megaphone, portable speaker or even a trumpet.\nLet’s sound the alarm together to wake the Finnish government up!\n\nThe situation is urgent: Gaza is pushed to famine. The illegal siege continues.\n\nFinnish citizens are sailing with the Global Sumud Flotilla in international waters to break the blockade. There is a real risk of Israeli interception in the coming days.\n\nThe Finnish government is saying aid must reach Gaza — now it’s time for them to wake up and act on it by:\n\nEnsuring the safe arrival of the Global Sumud Flotilla and protect the safety of all crew members so that they safely reach Gaza.\n\nTaking concrete measures to end the illegal siege and genocide in Gaza — with sanctions, trade embargoes, and by recognizing Palestine\n\nUpholding international law and act now that it is violated.\n\nNo racist, sexist, or discriminatory signs or slogans.\nDe-escalators will be present — reach up to them if you feel unsafe or concerned.	\N	sumud.office	sumud.office	2025-09-24 03:00:00	\N	\N	2025-09-24 03:00:00	https://www.sumud.fi/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/WhatsApp-Image-2025-09-23-at-18.34.40.jpeg	\N	[]	[]	[]
